description: This is a React component source file that implements an admin dashboard interface for managing visitor logs, visitors, hosts, and notifications in a visitor check-in system. It includes data fetching, filtering, and action handling for different data tables.

methods.name: formatDate
methods.description: Formats a string date into a localized string; returns empty if input is null or undefined.

methods.name: fetcher
methods.description: Utility function to fetch and parse JSON data from the backend API endpoint.

methods.name: AdminDashboard
methods.description: Main React component that renders the entire admin dashboard, fetching data from APIs and displaying it in data tables with filtering and action controls.
